We then reflect the diagram over the $x$-axis:

[asy]
unitsize(1 cm);

pair A, B, C, Ap,  Bp, Cp;

A = (0,2);
B = (-3,2);
C = (-3,0);
Ap = reflect((0,0),(1,0))*(A);
Bp = reflect((0,0),(1,0))*(B);
Cp = reflect((0,0),(1,0))*(C);

draw(A--B--C--cycle);
draw(Ap--Bp--Cp--cycle);
draw((-3.5,0)--(3.5,0));
draw((0,-3.5)--(0,3.5));

